This associated Ward identities are now violated,
and longitudinal modes of the tower of  are produced.

The real problem is that the truncation of the Virasoro algebra
we have defined does not close. In order to have a unitary theory
on the lattice, we would need to protect  with some
exact symmetries, and it is not at all obvious what these symmetries
might be. 

